long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Let's face it, 2020 hasn't started off particularly well. Climate Change is now unfolding exactly how scientists predicted many year ago, and Iran and USA are in serious conflict.
To lighten the day, add this app to your Chrome browser to replace all instances of Scott Morrison and friends with more apt names on web pages.
